es.ull.isaatc.function
Class LinearFunction

java.lang.Object
  es.ull.isaatc.function.TimeFunction
      es.ull.isaatc.function.LinearFunction

public class LinearFunction
extends TimeFunction

Represents the linear function: A·x + B. Thus, two parameters are required: A (scale) and B (shift).

Author:
Iván Castilla Rodríguez
